Hello. This is my new de_fusion map. After 2 years. 
I hope you like, because I made it in 5 days. The next map will be in Cristmas, maybe. 
Bye all.

For installation, save the map in your directory 
(ex. C:\Programmi\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\YOURNICKNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps)

Have Fun ;)

P.s. For every tips, I will read the comments but I can't change anything now. Your tips will need for the next...
